title: Counter Attack - Leo Kessler(N00DL35)
description: It was 1944 and Occupied France was on the verge of collapse as the avenging Allied armies scythed through Normandy. SS Assault Regiment Wotan, the most deadly of the elite, knew that they were marching to their doom as they raced to spearhead a counter-attack through the Falaise Gap. It was a trap - but Wotan would never surrender and so they found themselves in a desperate race with time to return to Germany and defend the very frontiers of the Reich from their pursuers.
